name: Infinity Run (pymaster)
description:
This is a unique infinite runner game, where you guide your robot across a series of challenging levels. But don't worry if you fall, since An End is a New Beginning. Created by Aditya, an eighth grader, this game was submitted to the Brackey's Game Jam 2023.1.

This game uses AI generated sprites and music. A full description can be found in my end credits.
